# Mermaid + MPE

## Preferred stack

1. `theme: "base"` + `themeVariables` + `themeCSS` in `mermaidConfig`
2. VS Code: `"markdown-preview-enhanced.mermaidTheme": "default"` (not `"dark"`)
3. Optional CSS overlay: experimental `cpp-modern-v3-diagrams` / `--md-diagram-*` — secondary to config

`themes/mpe/released/<slug>/config.js` is a **full** Crossnote config (`katexConfig`, `mathjaxConfig`, `mermaidConfig`). Install by pasting it over `%USERPROFILE%\.crossnote\config.js` (same file shape). Keep `"startOnLoad": false` inside `mermaidConfig`. Released packages must ship this file.

## Config paths

- Dark: `themes/mpe/released/cpp-modern/config.js` (`darkMode: true`)
- Light: `themes/mpe/released/cpp-modern-light/config.js` (`darkMode: false`)
- Lumina Aurora dark/light: `themes/mpe/released/lumina-v5-aurora/config.js` / `lumina-v5-aurora-light/config.js`

## Critical fixes

| Symptom | Fix |
| ------- | --- |
| Gray pills behind edge labels | `edgeLabelBackground` / `labelBackground` / state `labelBackgroundColor` → `transparent` |
| ER white zebra rows | `themeCSS` on `.row-rect-odd>path:first-child` / `.row-rect-even>path:first-child` (not only `attributeBackgroundColor*`) |
| Gantt / pie / mindmap / journey | Prefer vars in `released/*/config.js` → `mermaidConfig` + `themeCSS`; mindmap needs dark `.section-N` fills |
| Quadrant black labels | `quadrant1TextFill`…`quadrant4TextFill` (not `quadrantLabelFill`) |

## Light pitfalls

| Symptom | Fix |
| ------- | --- |
| Quadrant point labels invisible | Dark `quadrantPointTextFill` + `.data-point text` |
| Journey faces muddy | `.face` pale fill + dark stroke |
| Mindmap root unreadable | White text on root; override after `.mindmap-node` |
| ER zebra wrong / washed | Vars **and** `.row-rect-*` in `themeCSS` |
| Gantt bars blend into bands | Deeper task fills than section bands |

