## Commit

After a substantive Mermaid config / docs fix (new diagram type tuning, ER/`themeCSS` fix, promote-ready config.js), **commit** that unit. See `repo-theme-map` — commit after major changes. Skip commits for trivial one-line typos mid-iteration.
